	* code/php/user_validation.php: - we now save user groups defined
	by the admin to a new session variable	 'adminUserGroups' (note
	that these 'user groups' are groups of	 *database users* saved by
	the admin using the user management interface,	 not groups of
	*references* saved by a particular user) - 'getUserGroups()'
	function calls now require an additional parameter to
	descriminate between calls originating from 'search.php' and calls
	coming from 'users.php'

