	* code/php/index.php: - replaced the fixed string 'polar & marine'
	with the '$scientificFieldDescriptor'	variable (which is defined
	in 'ini.inc.php') - added '$oldQuery' parameter to
	'showPageHeader()' function call - added link to 'import_csa.php'
	in features list - added 'selected' field selector to
	'myRefsSearch' form - modified the section containing pre-defined
	search links: the links now make   use of search features provided
	by the new 'show.php' script

