	(as well as the sort popups) will include   any user specific
	fields, otherwise not - re-arranged elements of the
	'advancedSearch' form so that user specific fields   now group
	together at the bottom of the form - adopted the 'selectDistinct()'
	function so that it handles querying of user   specific fields
	correctly

